3: //! -------------------------------------------
4: //! Module 34: Enrichment & Data-Quality Pipeline
5: //!
6: //! This module defines a pluggable enrichment pipeline that is executed
7: //! on top of an asynchronous message stream (Kafka in production, but the
8: //! exact transport is intentionally abstracted behind `tokio` channels).
9: //!
10: //! ‣ Strategy-pattern based `Enricher` implementations can be hot-swapped
11: //!   at runtime without service downtime.  
12: //! ‣ A `QualityGate` performs data-quality validation after every stage
13: //!   and automatically routes invalid events to a quarantine topic.  
14: //! ‣ Metrics are exported via `opentelemetry` while structured logging
15: //!   captures detailed lineage information for auditability.
16: //
17: //! Compile-time features
18: //! ---------------------
19: //! ```toml
20: //! [dependencies]
21: //! anyhow        = "1"
22: //! async-trait   = "0.1"
23: //! chrono        = { version = "0.4", features = ["serde"] }
24: //! futures       = "0.3"
25: //! opentelemetry = { version = "0.20", features = ["metrics"] }
26: //! serde         = { version = "1", features = ["derive"] }
27: //! tokio         = { version = "1", features = ["macros", "rt-multi-thread", "time"] }
28: //! tracing       = "0.1"
29: //! ```
